                                            __cfduid
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Domain" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Domain</span>
                                            <a href="https://learninghub.nhs.uk/" data-cke-saved-href="https://learninghub.nhs.uk/"
                                               title="https://learninghub.nhs.uk">learninghub.nhs.uk</a>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Purpose" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Purpose</span>
                                            (.addtoany.com domain) Used to track user initiated social media postings.
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Expiry" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Expiry</span>
                                            One month
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="nhsuk-table__row" role="row">
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Cookie name" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Cookie name</span>
                                            .AspNetCore.Cookies
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Domain" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Domain</span>
                                            <a href="https://learninghub.nhs.uk/" data-cke-saved-href="https://learninghub.nhs.uk/"
                                               title="https://learninghub.nhs.uk">learninghub.nhs.uk</a>
                                        </td>
                                        <td><span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Purpose</span></td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Expiry" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Expiry</span>
                                            Session
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr class="nhsuk-table__row" role="row">
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Cookie name" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Cookie name</span>
                                            ARRAffinitySameSite
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Domain" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Domain</span>
                                            <a href="http://learninghubnhsuk-auth-prod.azurewebsites.net/" data-cke-saved-href="http://learninghubnhsuk-auth-prod.azurewebsites.net/" title="http://learninghubnhsuk-auth-prod.azurewebsites.net">learninghubnhsuk-auth-prod.azurewebsites.net</a>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Purpose" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Purpose</span>                                           
                                             This cookie is set by Windows Azure cloud, and is used for load balancing to make sure
                                             the visitor page requests are routed to the same server in any browsing.
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Expiry" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Expiry</span>
                                            Session
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>                                    
                                    <tr class="nhsuk-table__row" role="row">
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Cookie name" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Cookie name</span>
                                            <span class="dont-break-out">AspNetCore.Antiforgery.McPAzhLGOYg</span>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Domain" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Domain</span>
                                            <p>
                                                <a href="https://auth.learninghub.nhs.uk/" data-cke-saved-href="https://auth.learninghub.nhs.uk/" 
                                                title="https://auth.learninghub.nhs.uk">auth.learninghub.nhs.uk</a>
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Purpose" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Purpose</span>
                                            <p>Collaborates with .AspNetCore.Session to provide protection against Cross-site request forgery (also known as XSRF or CSRF).</p>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Expiry" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Expiry</span>
                                            Session
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>                  
                                    <tr class="nhsuk-table__row" role="row">
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Cookie name" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Cookie name</span>
                                            idsrv.session
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Domain" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Domain</span>
                                            <p>
                                                <a href="https://auth.learninghub.nhs.uk/" data-cke-saved-href="https://auth.learninghub.nhs.uk/"
                                                   title="https://auth.learninghub.nhs.uk">auth.learninghub.nhs.uk</a>
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Purpose" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Purpose</span>                                           
                                            This cookie is derived from the main authentication cookie, and it used for the
                                            check session endpoint for browser-based JavaScript clients at signout time.                                            
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Expiry" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Expiry</span>
                                            Session
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </details>
            </section>
            <section>
                <div>
                    <h2>Cookies that measure website use</h2>
                    <p>
                        We also like to use analytics cookies. These cookies store anonymous information about how you
                        use our website, such as which pages you visit or what you click on.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <details class="nhsuk-details">
                    <summary class="nhsuk-details__summary">
                        <span class="nhsuk-details__summary-text">
                            List of cookies
                            that measure website use
                        </span>
                    </summary>
                    <div class="nhsuk-details__text">
                        <div class="nhsuk-table-responsive">
                            <table class="nhsuk-table">
                                <caption class="nhsuk-table__caption nhsuk-u-visually-hidden">
                                    Cookie names and purposes
                                </caption>
                                <thead class="nhsuk-table__head">
                                    <tr class="nhsuk-table__row" role="row">
                                        <th class="nhsuk-table__header" role="columnheader" scope="col">Cookie name</th>
                                        <th class="nhsuk-table__header" role="columnheader" scope="col">Domain</th>
                                        <th class="nhsuk-table__header" role="columnheader" scope="col">Purpose</th>
                                        <th class="nhsuk-table__header" role="columnheader" scope="col">Expiry</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody class="nhsuk-table__body">
                                    <tr class="nhsuk-table__row" role="row">
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Cookie name" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Cookie name</span>
                                            Google analytics cookies
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Domain" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Domain</span>
                                            <a href="https://learninghub.nhs.uk/"
                                               data-cke-saved-href="https://learninghub.nhs.uk/"
                                               title="https://learninghub.nhs.uk">learninghub.nhs.uk</a>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell" data-label="Purpose" role="cell">
                                            <span class="nhsuk-table-responsive__heading">Purpose</span>
                                            <div class="flex-box-vertical">
                                                <p>
